    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=607984656221995780&sectionId=607984837298487863)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIRMgOhI3i_childItem_0","label":"ggIRMgOhI3i_childItem_0","default":"<p>Home &gt; Health&gt; Shoulder Health</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEZM87GTMw_text","label":"ggEZM87GTMw_text","default":"Top Orthopedic Surgeons: \"This Is the Fastest Way to Relieve Shoulder Pain for Good\""},{"type":"html","id":"gg_ZJRkI3JH_childItem_0","label":"gg_ZJRkI3JH_childItem_0","default":"<p>Mon. Oct. 27th, 2025 | 11:11 am EST -</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggo3t4G28-W_text","label":"ggo3t4G28-W_text","default":"Written by Dr. Schilling, Orthopedic Surgeon, MD |&nbsp;"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqTO7_T-55_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggqTO7_T-55_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/1769692671692__3.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQJnLMx1Y__text","label":"ggQJnLMx1Y__text","default":"<i>Dear Friend With Shoulder Pain,</i>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpAansp9bG_text","label":"ggpAansp9bG_text","default":"If you're reading this with your shoulder throbbing..."},{"type":"html","id":"ggUbyTVsBM6_text","label":"ggUbyTVsBM6_text","default":"If you can't sleep on your side anymore..."},{"type":"html","id":"ggdbkvPbtnM_text","label":"ggdbkvPbtnM_text","default":"If reaching for a cup in the cabinet feels like someone's stabbing you with a hot knife..."},{"type":"html","id":"ggYGRSVI_tj_text","label":"ggYGRSVI_tj_text","default":"Then what I'm about to share could save you from invasive procedures, endless physical therapy, and a lifetime of limitation."},{"type":"html","id":"gghJUoNsFcO_text","label":"gghJUoNsFcO_text","default":"But I need to warn you:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggu7rknwDj5_text","label":"ggu7rknwDj5_text","default":"What you're about to read will make you angry."},{"type":"html","id":"ggsmEviq6Hc_text","label":"ggsmEviq6Hc_text","default":"Because the method I discovered has been deliberately hidden from you."},{"type":"html","id":"ggueN3HKgdm_text","label":"ggueN3HKgdm_text","default":"Not because it doesn't work."},{"type":"html","id":"ggV4nVMbby7_text","label":"ggV4nVMbby7_text","default":"But because it works TOO well."},{"type":"html","id":"ggtpk1FB3dk_text","label":"ggtpk1FB3dk_text","default":"And when a $73 billion shoulder invasive procedures industry sees something that could make 87% of their procedures unnecessary..."},{"type":"html","id":"ggXdieB6cdw_text","label":"ggXdieB6cdw_text","default":"They don't celebrate."},{"type":"html","id":"gg-i7hYmxOk_text","label":"gg-i7hYmxOk_text","default":"They attack."},{"type":"html","id":"ggl690LdzyJ_text","label":"ggl690LdzyJ_text","default":"<strong>My Name is Dr. Blane Schilling.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxoAyRUVXs_text","label":"ggxoAyRUVXs_text","default":"I'm an orthopedic surgeon with 23 years of experience."},{"type":"html","id":"gg1u2lkA0Co_text","label":"gg1u2lkA0Co_text","default":"I've performed over 3,000 shoulder surgeries."},{"type":"html","id":"ggJaFbdw05v_text","label":"ggJaFbdw05v_text","default":"I've taught surgical techniques at Johns Hopkins."},{"type":"html","id":"ggE_mX35yFu_text","label":"ggE_mX35yFu_text","default":"And until 18 months ago, I believed everything I'd been taught about rotator cuff degeneration."},{"type":"html","id":"ggXQiwvoQqN_text","label":"ggXQiwvoQqN_text","default":"<strong>THE NIGHT EVERYTHING CHANGED...</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7zw7BlkT5_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg7zw7BlkT5_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/1769109049451_01_4.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaMloEySbv_text","label":"ggaMloEySbv_text","default":"Then at 3:17 AM on a Tuesday morning, everything changed."},{"type":"html","id":"ggXOFGdKFLo_text","label":"ggXOFGdKFLo_text","default":"I woke up to a crash from our bathroom."},{"type":"html","id":"ggUQs0TFDQJ_text","label":"ggUQs0TFDQJ_text","default":"Racing in, I found my wife Sarah on the floor, sobbing."},{"type":"html","id":"ggW-jMsfnNf_text","label":"ggW-jMsfnNf_text","default":"The bottle of Percocet had fallen from the top shelf."},{"type":"html","id":"gg4cWlFRQ2r_text","label":"gg4cWlFRQ2r_text","default":"She couldn't reach it."},{"type":"html","id":"ggtbNra9i0x_text","label":"ggtbNra9i0x_text","default":"Her shoulder - the one that had been \"manageable\" for months - had finally given out."},{"type":"html","id":"ggIIFnVNPfS_text","label":"ggIIFnVNPfS_text","default":"\"I can't do it anymore,\" she whispered. \"I can't even get my own painkillers.\""},{"type":"html","id":"ggPK0-ADWBt_text","label":"ggPK0-ADWBt_text","default":"Sarah is a critical care nurse. Was a critical care nurse. For 19 years, she worked in the ICU - lifting, turning, and repositioning patients who couldn't move themselves."},{"type":"html","id":"ggOin8X8R-h_text","label":"ggOin8X8R-h_text","default":"The wear on her shoulders was gradual, then sudden."},{"type":"html","id":"gg8-IR9jKfg_text","label":"gg8-IR9jKfg_text","default":"Now she couldn't lift her arm past 45 degrees."},{"type":"html","id":"ggEumrlyAvj_text","label":"ggEumrlyAvj_text","default":"<strong>But Here's What Destroyed Me:</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSHo0RvwlR_text","label":"ggSHo0RvwlR_text","default":"When I tried to help her up, she screamed."},{"type":"html","id":"ggPTZMErDeE_text","label":"ggPTZMErDeE_text","default":"I touched her shoulder."},{"type":"html","id":"ggAvvhueuOc_text","label":"ggAvvhueuOc_text","default":"That's all it took."},{"type":"html","id":"ggsun1C-rgi_text","label":"ggsun1C-rgi_text","default":"We hadn't hugged - really hugged - in 4 months."},{"type":"html","id":"gg5t8uMXhgM_text","label":"gg5t8uMXhgM_text","default":"Every embrace ended in wincing."},{"type":"html","id":"ggAQFMyls5G_text","label":"ggAQFMyls5G_text","default":"Every attempted comfort became another reminder of what we'd lost."},{"type":"html","id":"ggvXAacaOwW_text","label":"ggvXAacaOwW_text","default":"The woman who once lifted 200-pound patients couldn't hug her own husband."},{"type":"html","id":"gg2As2ggWqg_text","label":"gg2As2ggWqg_text","default":"And I just stood there."},{"type":"html","id":"ggirnH8ztlW_text","label":"ggirnH8ztlW_text","default":"Useless."},{"type":"html","id":"ggs3uWKXNVn_text","label":"ggs3uWKXNVn_text","default":"An orthopedic surgeon who couldn't even help his own wife."},{"type":"html","id":"ggQyEVd5Xo5_text","label":"ggQyEVd5Xo5_text","default":"I'd tried everything my training taught me. Physical therapy. Cortisone shots. Ice. Heat. TENS units."},{"type":"html","id":"gg-xQgSUT5B_text","label":"gg-xQgSUT5B_text","default":"Nothing worked for more than a few hours."},{"type":"html","id":"ggZZqwbLRh1_text","label":"ggZZqwbLRh1_text","default":"The \"experts\" weren't any better:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggp-mRdTYSn_text","label":"ggp-mRdTYSn_text","default":"An orthopedic surgeon who couldn't even help his own wife."},{"type":"html","id":"ggqOr3ZxIG1_childItem_0","label":"ggqOr3ZxIG1_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Her physical therapist?</strong> Stretched and strengthened twice a week for $200 a pop. The relief lasted about as long as the car ride home.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqOr3ZxIG1_childItem_1","label":"ggqOr3ZxIG1_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>Pain management doctor?</strong> Pumped her full of cortisone shots that made her gain 25 pounds and feel like a zombie.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqOr3ZxIG1_childItem_2","label":"ggqOr3ZxIG1_childItem_2","default":"<p><strong>The shoulder surgeon?</strong> Wanted to slice her open for a $35,000 procedure with a 40% failure rate.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMuv4RiHUY_text","label":"ggMuv4RiHUY_text","default":"That night, something inside me snapped."},{"type":"html","id":"ggX4hHcXB8O_text","label":"ggX4hHcXB8O_text","default":"I wasn't going to watch the woman I love turn into a prescription drug statistic."},{"type":"html","id":"ggxElBJxMg8_text","label":"ggxElBJxMg8_text","default":"I wasn't going to let some surgeon use her as a Mercedes payment."},{"type":"html","id":"ggSdPdMajre_text","label":"ggSdPdMajre_text","default":"<strong>I went to war with everything I thought I knew about shoulder pain.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_oAMN5Dur_text","label":"gg_oAMN5Dur_text","default":"A revolutionary device is making headlines for reducing 99.8% of Shoulder pain in just minutes."},{"type":"html","id":"ggrLMalAwzP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggrLMalAwzP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/1769110586572_product_with_box_mockup.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZmLvq_TMg_text","label":"ggZmLvq_TMg_text","default":"After 24 months of research and over 2,400 patients studied, experts finally created a non-invasive method to alleviate Shoulder pain all packed into one powerful at-home device."},{"type":"html","id":"ggf4H8wMLnY_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggf4H8wMLnY_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/1762531073177_1760523534607_eh.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkXlL0fgyk_text","label":"ggkXlL0fgyk_text","default":"Here are the life-changing results people over 50 have experienced :"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpi5v42SvU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggpi5v42SvU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/1769110656859_08a.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-mwPgIE7__text","label":"gg-mwPgIE7__text","default":"Individual results may very*"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGG4VM0Aao_text","label":"ggGG4VM0Aao_text",